Tyndale Open Study Notes — Multilingual Translations

The English Tyndale Open Study Notes are © Tyndale House Publishers,
distributed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
International License (CC BY-SA 4.0).
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Official non-English translations were sourced from BurritoTruck on
Door43 (https://git.door43.org/BurritoTruck), also under CC BY-SA 4.0:
  fr_tsn — Notes d'étude Tyndale en français
  pt_tsn — Notas de Estudo Tyndale em português
  es_tsn — Notas de Estudio Tyndale en español

A subset of verses lacking official non-English translations were
translated to match Tyndale's content by Anthropic's Claude (Sonnet),
and are released under the same CC BY-SA 4.0 license.

Verses for which no translation is yet available fall back to the
English Tyndale text inline (same chapter file) so the reader always
sees scholarly content.

Sources:
  https://tyndaleopenresources.com/
  https://git.door43.org/BurritoTruck/
